doctype html
head
    meta(charset="utf-8")
    meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="IE=edge")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1")
    title(deckrank.co: About Us)
    link(rel="stylesheet",
        href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.4/css/bootstrap.min.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", type="text/css", href="css/rozinah.css")
    include mixpanel.jade
body
    include header.jade
    div.container-fluid
      div.form-group(id="faq")
        h3 Frequently Asked Questions
            h4 What is deckrank?
            |It's a simple tool that lets you quickly create a poll,
            |get multiple people to vote and see the ranking of options.
            br
            br
            h4 In what situations will I need deckrank?
            |Here's an example.
            |I want to have lunch with a group of friends.
            |To help coordinate, I do the following:
            ol
                li Create a poll with different options for meeting time
                li Create another poll with restaurant options
                li Get my friends to vote on the above polls
            |Voila! Now, my friends and I will be able to see the resulting ranking of
            |options. In a deckrank-less universe, this would've turned into a
            |chaotic chain of emails.
            br
            br
            h4 I kind of get the idea, could you show me some polls so I can explain it to my grandmother?
            |Sure thing, check out&nbsp
            a(href="https://www.twitter.com/deckrank")
                @deckrank
            |&nbspon Twitter.
      div.form-group(id="about")
        h3 About
        p
            |deckrank is authored by Sunil Kowlgi (
            a(href="https://www.twitter.com/kowlgi") @kowlgi
            |) and friends.
      div.form-group(id="contact")
        h3 Contact
        form(role="form", id="contactform", method="post", action="/contact")
            div.form-group.col-md-7
              label(for="title") Your email
              input(type="text", class="form-control", id="title",
                    name="title", placeholder="Your email...",
                    required="required", maxlength="40")
            div.form-group.col-md-7
              label(for="Description") Feedback
              textarea(class="form-control" id="description", name="description",
                rows="1",
                placeholder="Your message...",
                required="required",
                maxlength="140")
            div.form-group.col-md-7
                button(type="submit", value="submit", class="btn btn-default")
                  |Send Feedback
    include footer.jade
    script(src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.3/jquery.min.js")
    script(src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.4/js/bootstrap.min.js")
    script(src="js/rozinah.js")
